'''Starfarer''' is a PC-only [[Special:MyLanguage/worlds|world]] created by Waai!. It was published in 2021. It contains 4 compartments within a train that is traversing through a field of shooting stars.

==Design==
[[File:Starfarer-Resturant-Compartment.jpg|thumb|Restaurant Compartment found in Starfarer]]
The interior is designed after that found in old trains. It is seemingly floating through the night sky. Looking outside clouds and shooting stars can be seen passing, implying that the train is moving forward.
Opening the [[Special:MyLanguage/Menus|VRChat Menu]] reveals additional world options on the walls of each of the doors connecting the different compartments.

==Compartments==
The world is split into 4 compartments of 3 different types. They are separated by sliding doors.

===Main Compartment===
This Main Compartment is the one that also serves as a spawn area. It has couches and tables around a carpet with a moon motif.

=== Restaurant Compartment===
Next to the Main Compartment, in the driving direction, is the Restaurant Compartment. On its left are seating arrangements for groups, while the other side consists of one elongated table attached to the wall with bar stools placed to be seated looking towards the windows.

===Sleeping Compartment===
2 compartments that are within compartments opposite of the driving direction contain several individual smaller compartments with bedding and some seating arrangements. It can be great to have more private conversations in smaller groups. Along its left side is a small corridor linking them all up.